# Console batch simples com observabilidade

## 1) Objetivo
Padronizar apps console focados em processos batch simples, com logging estruturado e tracing.

## 2) Estrutura de pastas
```
src/
  App/
    Program.cs
    Jobs/
  Application/
    Services/
  Infrastructure/
    Observability/
deploy/
  Dockerfile
tests/
  Unit/
  Integration/
```

## 3) Pacotes recomendados
- Serilog.Extensions.Hosting, Serilog.Sinks.Console
- OpenTelemetry.Extensions.Hosting
- OpenTelemetry.Instrumentation.Http
- OpenTelemetry.Exporter.OpenTelemetryProtocol
- MediatR (para orquestrar jobs/comandos)

## 4) Configuracao (Program.cs)
```csharp
using Microsoft.Extensions.Hosting;
using Serilog;
using OpenTelemetry.Trace;

Host.CreateDefaultBuilder(args)
    .UseSerilog((ctx, cfg) => cfg.ReadFrom.Configuration(ctx.Configuration))
    .ConfigureServices((ctx, services) =>
    {
        services.AddMediatR(cfg => cfg.RegisterServicesFromAssemblyContaining<Program>());
        services.AddOpenTelemetry()
            .WithTracing(t => t.AddHttpClientInstrumentation().AddSource("BatchJobs"));
        services.AddHostedService<ImportJob>();
    })
    .Build()
    .Run();
```

## 5) Exemplo de Job
```csharp
public class ImportJob : BackgroundService
{
    private readonly ILogger<ImportJob> _logger;
    public ImportJob(ILogger<ImportJob> logger) => _logger = logger;

    protected override async Task ExecuteAsync(CancellationToken stoppingToken)
    {
        _logger.LogInformation("Import job started");
        // processamento aqui
        await Task.Delay(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(1), stoppingToken);
        _logger.LogInformation("Import job finished");
    }
}
```

### Job com entrada externa, validacao e MediatR
```csharp
public record ImportCustomersCommand(string FilePath) : IRequest;

public class ImportCustomersHandler : IRequestHandler<ImportCustomersCommand>
{
  private readonly ILogger<ImportCustomersHandler> _logger;
  private readonly ICustomerRepository _repo;

  public ImportCustomersHandler(ILogger<ImportCustomersHandler> logger, ICustomerRepository repo)
  {
    _logger = logger;
    _repo = repo;
  }

  public async Task Handle(ImportCustomersCommand request, CancellationToken ct)
  {
    if (!File.Exists(request.FilePath))
      throw new FileNotFoundException("Input file not found", request.FilePath);

    using var stream = File.OpenRead(request.FilePath);
    using var reader = new StreamReader(stream);

    while (!reader.EndOfStream)
    {
      var line = await reader.ReadLineAsync();
      if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(line)) continue;

      var columns = line.Split(';');
      var customer = new Customer(columns[0], columns[1], columns[2]);
      await _repo.AddAsync(customer, ct);
    }

    _logger.LogInformation("Customers imported from {File}", request.FilePath);
  }
}
```

